HEADWORD: Voltmeter
<hw>Volt"me`ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[2d
<ets>volt</ets> + <ets>-meter</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(elec.)</fld> <def>An
